# Node Health Check Script

This repository contains a simple Bash script that checks the health of a Linux node by reporting basic system metrics.

## What the Script Does

The script checks and displays:
- Disk usage
- Memory usage
- CPU load
- System uptime

This is useful for quick diagnostics, monitoring practice, and learning basic system health checks as part of DevOps fundamentals.

## Requirements

- Linux system
- Bash shell

